sequenceDiagram
	autonumber
	participant Dev as Developer
	participant Repo as BlogAI repository
	participant Local as Local secret files
	participant Host as SmarterASP deployment folder
	participant App as BlogEngine.NET app

	Dev->>Repo: Pull latest committed session state
	Dev->>Local: Copy *.example files to real secret files
	Dev->>Local: Set BlogEngine connection string and ReloadEndpointKey
	Dev->>App: Build and run locally
	App-->>Dev: Starts with externalized secrets
	Dev->>Host: Deploy application files
	Dev->>Host: Upload connectionStrings.config
	Dev->>Host: Upload appSettings.secrets.config
	Host->>App: Restart application
	App-->>Dev: Site and admin login validate
